snippet: Mitt Romney keeps his focus on President Obama.
abstract: Mitt Romney keeps his focus on President Obama.
lead_paragraph: DERRY, N.H. - Mitt Romney came to Derry, N.H., on Saturday morning, and after a rough start in the state - a phlegmatic McCain endorsement, some less-than-enthusiastic crowds- he finally seemed to know his audience.

headline.main: Romney Urges Supporters Not to Be Overconfident
